\c 10
\s Izibhebhe zamatshe zesibili zemithetho elitshumi
\p
\v 1 Ngalesosikhathi iN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kimi: Zibazele izibhebhe ezimbili zamatshe njengezakuqala, wenyukele kimi entabeni\x + Eks. 34.1,2.\x*, uzenzele umtshokotsho wezigodo\x + Eks. 25.10.\x*.
\v 2 Ngizabhala-ke phezu kwezibhebhe amazwi ayesezibhebheni zakuqala owazibulalayo, uzibeke emtshokotshweni\x + Eks. 25.16,21.\x*.
\v 3 Ngasengisenza umtshokotsho ngesihlahla sesinga\x + Eks. 25.10. 37.1.\x*, ngabaza izibhebhe ezimbili zamatshe njengezakuqala, ngenyukela entabeni, lezibhebhe ezimbili zisesandleni sami\x + Eks. 34.4.\x*.
\v 4 Yasibhala ezibhebheni njengokubhala kwakuqala, imilayo elitshumi\x + Eks. 34.28.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayikhuluma kini entabeni iphakathi komlilo\x + Eks. 20.1.\x* ngosuku lokuhlangana\x + 9.10.\x*; njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yanginika zona.
\v 5 Ngasengiphenduka ngisehla entabeni\x + Eks. 34.29.\x*, ngazifaka izibhebhe emtshokotshweni engangiwenzile\x + Eks. 40.20.\x*. Njalo zikhona lapho, njengokungilaya kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1 Kho. 8.9.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesuka eBeyerothi-Bene-Jakani\x + Nani 33.31.\x*, baya eMosera\x + Nani 33.30.\x*; uAroni wafela lapho, wangcwatshwa khona\x + Nani 20.28. 33.38.\x*; indodana yakhe uEleyazare wasebenza njengompristi esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 7 Besuka lapho, baya eGudigoda; basuka eGudigoda, baya eJotibatha, ilizwe lezifula zamanzi\x + Nani 33.32,33.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Ngalesosikhathi iN\nd kosi\nd* yehlukanisa isizwe sakoLevi\x + Nani 3.6. 8.14. 16.9.\x* ukuthi sithwale umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Nani 4.5,15.\x*, ukuthi sime phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, siyikhonze\x + 17.12. 18.5,7.\x*, sibusise ebizweni layo, kuze kube lamuhla\x + Levi 9.22.\x*.
\v 9 Ngalokhu uLevi kalasabelo lelifa kanye labafowabo; iN\nd kosi\nd* iyilifa lakhe, njengokuthembisa kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho kuye\x + Nani 18.20.\x*.
\v 10 Mina ngasengihlala entabeni njengensuku zendulo, insuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane\x + 9.18.\x*; leN\nd kosi\nd* yangizwa langalesosikhathi; iN\nd kosi\nd* kayithandanga ukukubhubhisa\x + 9.19.\x*.
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Sukuma, uhambe phambi kwabantu, ukuze bangene badle ilifa lelizwe engafunga kuboyise ukubanika lona\x + Eks. 32.34. 33.1.\x*.
\s Lokho iN\nd kosi\nd* ekufuna kuIsrayeli
\p
\v 12 Khathesi-ke, Israyeli, kuyini iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekufuna kuwe\x + Mika 6.8.\x*, ngaphandle kokuyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 6.2.\x*, ukuhamba ngendlela zayo zonke\x + 5.33.\x*, lokuyithanda, lokuyikhonza iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ngenhliziyo yakho yonke langomphefumulo wakho wonke\x + 6.5.\x*,
\v 13 ukugcina imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd* lezimiso zayo engikulaya zona lamuhla, ukuthi kukulungele\x + 6.24.\x*?
\v 14 Khangela, amazulu, lezulu lamazulu ngaweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Hlab. 115.16. 1 Kho. 8.27. Hlab. 148.4.\x*, umhlaba lakho konke okukuwo\x + Eks. 19.5. Hlab. 24.1. Gen. 14.19.\x*.
\v 15 Kuphela iN\nd kosi\nd* yehlisela uthando lwayo phezu kwaboyihlo, ukubathanda, yakhetha inzalo yabo emva kwabo, \add ngitsho\add* lina phakathi kwazo zonke izizwe, njengalamuhla\x + 4.37. Dute. 7.7.\x*.
\v 16 Ngakho sokani ijwabu laphambili lenhliziyo yenu\x + 30.6. Jer. 4.4. Eks. 6.12.\x*, lingabe lisazenza lukhuni intamo zenu\x + 9.6.\x*.
\v 17 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu inguNkulunkulu wabonkulunkulu\x + Josh. 22.22. Hlab. 136.2. Dan. 2.47. 11.36.\x*, leNkosi yamakhosi\x + Isam. 17.14. 19.16.\x*, uNkulunkulu omkhulu, olamandla\x + 7.21.\x*, lowesabekayo\x + 7.21.\x*, ongemukeli ubuso \add bomuntu\add*, ongemukeli umvuzo\x + 2 Lan. 19.7. Jobe 34.19. Seb. 10.34. Roma 2.11. Gal. 2.6. Efe. 6.9. Kol. 3.25. 1 Pet. 1.17.\x*.
\v 18 Eyenza isahlulelo sentandane lomfelokazi, njalo ethanda owezizweni ngokumnika ukudla lezembatho\x + Hlab. 68.5; 146.9; Eks.22.22.\x*.
\v 19 Ngakho lizamthanda owezizweni, ngoba lalingabezizweni elizweni leGibhithe\x + Levi 19.33,34.\x*.
\v 20 Uzayesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, uyikhonze\x + 6.2,13.\x*, unamathele kuyo\x + 11.22. 13.4. 30.20.\x*, ufunge ngebizo layo\x + 6.2,13.\x*.
\v 21 Iludumo lwakho, njalo inguNkulunkulu wakho\x + Hlab.22.3. 109.1. Jer. 17.14.\x*, okwenzele lezizinto ezinkulu lezesabekayo, amehlo akho azibonileyo\x + 2 Sam. 7.23; Hlab. 106.21,22.\x*.
\v 22 Oyihlo behlela eGibhithe belabantu abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa\x + Gen. 46.27.\x*; khathesi-ke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ikwenzile waba njengenkanyezi zamazulu ngobunengi\x + Gen. 15.5. Dute.28.62. Neh. 9.23.\x*.